    prompt: 'Complete a formal meditation assessment with a qualified instructor to evaluate your current technique and receive personalized feedback',
    category: 'action',
    helpText: 'Professional evaluation of your meditation practice ensures you are developing proper technique and identifies specific areas for improvement that you might not notice on your own. Schedule a session with an experienced meditation teacher who can observe your posture, breathing, and approach to provide detailed feedback on your form and suggest personalized adjustments. This expert guidance helps prevent the development of bad habits and accelerates your progress by addressing technique issues early in your journey.'
  },
  {
    id: 'prompt-50',
    prompt: 'Complete a 10-day meditation intensive by practicing twice daily for 20 minutes each session',
    category: 'action',
    helpText: 'Committing to an intensive 10-day practice period demonstrates your dedication to serious meditation development and helps you experience the cumulative effects of sustained daily practice. Practice once in the morning and once in the evening for 20 minutes each, using the same technique throughout to develop deep familiarity and concentration. This intensive approach accelerates your progress significantly and builds the mental discipline necessary for advanced meditation practice while proving to yourself that you can maintain consistent commitment.'
  }
];</parameter>
